Package org.fluidity.foundation.jarjar

Stream protocol handler to work with resources inside JAR archives embedded in other JAR archives.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccessPermission
    Represents a permission to access nested archives.
    Handler
    Stream protocol handler to work with resources inside JAR archives embedded in other JAR archives, ad infinitum.
    Launcher
    Launches a main class from a JAR file using a class loader that can load classes from JAR files nested inside the main JAR.
    URLClassLoader
    Caching URL class loader that does not keep files or connections open.
